    <item>
      <title>帝亚吉欧销售下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/diageo-tanks-on-sales-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尊尼获加和斯米诺伏的生产商帝亚吉欧受到拉丁美洲、加勒比地区和美国经济放缓的打击。这导致这家英国酿酒商公布了自疫情以来的首次年度销售额下滑。周二早盘，该公司股价下跌近 10%。彭博社的 Sabah Meddings 在彭博电视上进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/diageo-tanks-on-sales-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科廷称美联储将在 9 月开始降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/fed-to-start-cutting-rates-heading-into-autumn-curtin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alti Tiedemann Global 首席投资官 Nancy Curtin 表示，她相信美联储将在“进入 9 月时”开始降息，她认为美国消费者数据的下滑并不意味着该国经济复苏的终结。Curtin 在彭博电视上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/fed-to-start-cutting-rates-heading-into-autumn-curtin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:17:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前花旗集团销售交易员在香港就 2019 年不公平解雇提起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ex-citigroup-sales-trader-sues-for-2019-unfair-dismissal-in-hk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团香港分公司的一名前交易员于 2019 年起诉该银行不当解雇，这一事件促使监管机构于 2022 年对这家美国银行处以 4460 万美元的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ex-citigroup-sales-trader-sues-for-2019-unfair-dismissal-in-hk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:01:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宵禁和抗议活动拖累经济发展，标普下调孟加拉国评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/s-p-cuts-bangladesh-ratings-after-curfew-protests-slow-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在孟加拉国政府实施宵禁以平息致命的学生抗议活动近两周后，由于该国外汇储备持续下降，标准普尔全球评级将其信用评级从 BB- 下调至 B+。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/s-p-cuts-bangladesh-ratings-after-curfew-protests-slow-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奢侈品继承人声称其 130 亿美元爱马仕财富已消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/luxury-heir-alleges-his-13-billion-hermes-fortune-has-vanished</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱马仕 (Hermès) 奢侈品财富的一位八十多岁继承人因计划将财产留给园丁而引发去年的争议，但他可能也没什么可以赠予的了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/luxury-heir-alleges-his-13-billion-hermes-fortune-has-vanished</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国补贴成本不断膨胀 彰显绿色发展挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/germany-s-ballooning-subsidy-costs-show-challenge-of-going-green</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国正不堪重负地承担不断膨胀的可再生能源补贴，这让世界各国政府开始思考他们还能支撑绿色投资多久。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/germany-s-ballooning-subsidy-costs-show-challenge-of-going-green</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决定前欧洲股市因稳健数据走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估该地区最大经济体的增长数据并等待本周晚些时候美国和英国央行的利率决定，欧洲股市小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油公司保持回购稳定，利润稳定后提高股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bp-keeps-buyback-steady-raises-dividend-as-profit-stabilizes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司 (BP Plc) 保持了股票回购步伐，并增加了股息，因为第二季度原油开采带来的强劲盈利抵消了其他业务部门的疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bp-keeps-buyback-steady-raises-dividend-as-profit-stabilizes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管德国经济意外下滑，欧元区经济增长仍超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-s-economic-growth-beats-forecasts-in-boost-for-euro-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区经济第二季度增长超过预期，主要国家的强劲扩张使该地区摆脱了德国意外经济萎缩的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-s-economic-growth-beats-forecasts-in-boost-for-euro-area</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：GDP 数据好坏参半，欧洲股市涨幅缩减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区主要经济体公布的国内生产总值数据好坏参半，令人对经济复苏步伐产生怀疑，欧洲股市缩减涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
